# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Exocore Backend — Docker build context exclusions
#
# The image is built from a PRE-COMPILED, OBFUSCATED `dist/` only.
# Everything in this list is intentionally kept out of the build
# context so it can never end up inside the runtime image.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# 🔒 The TypeScript sources MUST stay on the developer's machine.
#    Compile locally (`npm run build:secure`) → upload `dist/` only.
src
tsconfig.json
*.tsbuildinfo

# Local-only state, secrets, and logs.
node_modules
local-db
*.log
.env
.env.*
.git
.gitignore
.DS_Store
credentials.json
token.json

# Editor / OS clutter.
.vscode
.idea
*.swp
*.swo

# Don't bake the Dockerfile or its ignore list into the image itself.
Dockerfile
.dockerignore

# Project docs aren't needed inside the runtime image.
README.md
